        <div class="attr">Spouse</div>
        <div class="val">Svala</div>

        <div class="attr">Children</div>
        <div class="val">None mentioned</div>

        <div class="attr">Residence</div>
        <div class="val">Víðidal, Iceland</div>

        <div class="attr">Nationality</div>
        <div class="val">Icelandic</div>

        <div class="attr">Notable events</div>
        <div class="val">Joining <a href='/wiki/oddur'>Oddur's</a> household, managing Oddur's farm, marrying Svala, giving up chieftainship, accused of theft and manslaughter, his death</div>
